      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>breaded chicken </strong>and cook for 2 min on each side or until golden</p><p>Once golden, transfer the chicken to a baking tray (reserve the pan!) and put the tray in the oven for 14-15 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chicken schnitzel</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
