    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[170ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
