    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wipe the reserved pan clean (careful, it will be hot!) and return to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>shallot</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
