    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>schnitzel</strong> over the <strong>fries</strong> with the <strong>quick-pickled cucumber </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>creamy mustard sauce</strong> all over and season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
